{"title":"Java日志框架概况","date":"2019-08-28T14:26:52.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 28, 2019","L":"08/28/2019","MM-DD":"08-28"},"thumbnail":"post/Java/日志/Java日志框架概况/cover.jpg","link":"post/Java/日志/Java日志框架概况","categories":["Java","日志"],"updated":"2020-02-08T02:39:09.488Z","content":"<h1 id=\"java日志框架分类\">Java日志框架分类<a href=\"#java日志框架分类\" title=\"Java日志框架分类\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"日志门面框架\">日志门面框架<a href=\"#日志门面框架\" title=\"日志门面框架\"></a></h2><p>主要用于适配各种不同的底层日志实现框架，提供统一访问的API，充当门面</p>\n<ul><li><code>slf4j</code></li>\n<li><code>commons-logging</code></li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"日志实现框架\">日志实现框架<a href=\"#日志实现框架\" title=\"日志实现框架\"></a></h2><p>实现具体的记录日志的操作的框架</p>\n<ul><li><code>log4j</code></li>\n<li><code>log4j2</code></li>\n<li><code>logback</code></li>\n<li><code>java.util.logging</code></li>\n</ul><h1 id=\"共性\">共性<a href=\"#共性\" title=\"共性\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"组件\">组件<a href=\"#组件\" title=\"组件\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"logger\">Logger<a href=\"#logger\" title=\"Logger\"></a></h3><p>提供日志输出的<code>API</code>，但往往不做任何事，实际的操作都通过其他组件实现。</p>\n<h3 id=\"loggermanager\">LoggerManager<a href=\"#loggermanager\" title=\"LoggerManager\"></a></h3><p>组织管理所有<code>Logger</code>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"level\">Level<a href=\"#level\" title=\"Level\"></a></h3><p>日志级别。可通过设置日志级别，让高于高级别的日志进行输出，低于该级别的日志无法输出。</p>\n<h3 id=\"appender\">Appender<a href=\"#appender\" title=\"Appender\"></a></h3><p>日志输出目的地。通常可输出到<code>Console</code>, <code>File</code>, <code>Socket</code>等地方。</p>\n<h3 id=\"filter\">Filter<a href=\"#filter\" title=\"Filter\"></a></h3><p>日志过滤器。用于在日志输出前对其进行过滤。</p>\n<h3 id=\"formatter\">Formatter<a href=\"#formatter\" title=\"Formatter\"></a></h3><p>日志格式化。</p>\n<h3 id=\"层次\">层次<a href=\"#层次\" title=\"层次\"></a></h3><p><code>Logger</code>往往被组织成一个树状层次结构，每个<code>Logger</code>(除了<code>RootLogger</code>)都有一个<code>Parent Logger</code>。</p>\n<p><code>Logger</code>一般是通过名字来进行层次划分(使用<code>.</code>)。</p>\n<ul><li><code>cn.edu.njust.dao.UserDao</code>的<code>Parent Logger</code>为<code>cn.edu.njust.dao</code>(若不存在，则继续上溯，直到<code>RootLogger</code>)</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/Java/%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/Java%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5/1.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h3 id=\"继承性\">继承性<a href=\"#继承性\" title=\"继承性\"></a></h3><p>未经配置的<code>Child Logger</code>往往继承或加性继承（合并）了<code>Parent Logger</code>的一些配置，如<code>Level</code>，<code>Appender</code>，<code>Hierachy</code>等。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"配置文件整合","link":"post/其他/配置文件整合"},"next":{"title":"5-MyBatis缓存","link":"post/Java/MyBatis/5-MyBatis缓存"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/Java/日志/Java日志框架概况/","toc":[{"id":"java日志框架分类","title":"Java日志框架分类","index":"1","children":[{"id":"日志门面框架","title":"日志门面框架","index":"1.1"},{"id":"日志实现框架","title":"日志实现框架","index":"1.2"}]},{"id":"共性","title":"共性","index":"2","children":[{"id":"组件","title":"组件","index":"2.1","children":[{"id":"logger","title":"Logger","index":"2.1.1"},{"id":"loggermanager","title":"LoggerManager","index":"2.1.2"},{"id":"level","title":"Level","index":"2.1.3"},{"id":"appender","title":"Appender","index":"2.1.4"},{"id":"filter","title":"Filter","index":"2.1.5"},{"id":"formatter","title":"Formatter","index":"2.1.6"},{"id":"层次","title":"层次","index":"2.1.7"},{"id":"继承性","title":"继承性","index":"2.1.8"}]}]}]}